### Health
GET  http://localhost:3000/

### Simulate call.hangup (safe local test, no Telnyx API call)
POST http://localhost:3000/webhooks/telnyx/dev
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": {
    "event_type": "call.hangup",
    "payload": {
      "call_control_id": "test-call-001",
      "direction": "incoming",
      "from": "+15550001111",
      "to": "+15073085087"
    }
  }
}

